Entry-Name: .description

TEST STEPS

1. Go to Window/Preferences and select "One click" in Open mode settings;
2. Press Apply, OK;
3. Make single-click on class1 in Package Explorer;
4. Make sure that class1 editor has been opened;
5. Go to Window/Preferences and select "Double click" in Open mode settings;
6. Close class1 editor;
7. Try to do single-click on class1 - make sure that no editors have been opened. 
